metadata.name: Tarot Cards #00 The Fool
metadata.description:
What if tarot could be recreated in the modern world? It's a tarot card picture that I solved with that curiosity and my perspective.

*This is a personal interpretation.

[00 The Fool]

A young man in his 20s who dreams of starting actively (I focused on the image of beginning rather than the word fool)

Clothing> sweatshirt, logo on pattern, yellow sneakers Reinforced silhouette with jacket

The Fool, a young man in his 20s who is just starting a live broadcast with Bichon, has a fun and exciting start. he started his journey with a small pocket bag to go anywhere freely.
